    • toggleNodeMark

      void toggleNodeMark(PetrinetElement petrinetElement)
      Mark the node representing the element if it is has not been selected and unmark the former marked node (if there was one). If the provided node is already marked unmark it. If null is passed unmark the currently marked node.
      Parameters:
      petrinetElement - Element for which node should be marked / unmarked (null -> currently marked node is unmarked).
